<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Weekly Redmine issue to Email<small> 获取一周Redmine issue并发送Email</small></h1>
</div>
<h2><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-globe"></span> 我的周报</h2>
<br>
  <p>
    <% unless @auth.key.to_s.empty? %>
      <span><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up"></span> 您已提交过key</span>
      <a href="/user/<%=session['username']%>/remove_key"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-xs"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-link"></span> 移除Key?</button></a>
    <% else %>
      <form action="/" method="post"role="form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="key">Redmine Key:</label>
        <br>
        <input id="key" class="form-control" name="auth[key]" type="text" value="" style="width=90%"/>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">保存</button>
      </form>
      <br>
      <small><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span> Redmine key获取位置通常位于您的Redmine 》我的账号 》API访问键 》点击显示</small>
    <% end %>
  </p>
